0. You will need Node.js before hand
1. open gitbash and run npm install -g @angular/cli
2. then make sure you are in the correct directory for where you wish to create your project
3. run ng new examplename
4.then cd into your project
5.then run code . and the project will magically apear in vs code :)
6. If you want run the app on a browser run  ng serve --open
7. to stop it from running run ctrl c
